{"tid":2216154,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"亞太區百大美男美女︱四位香港男星上榜　呢位46歲TVB小生都有份","createTime":"2020-09-24T12:59:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-26T10:25:43.000Z","uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb1e5118820b46513df4a3c3b4c99c5d55858ba","tid":2216154,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T12:59:38.000Z","msg":"美國知名電影評論網站「TC Candler」每年都會舉辦「世界百大美男美女」選舉，為了打入內地市場近年更增設「亞太區」選舉。網站最近公布了新一屆的「亞太區百大最帥臉孔」入圍名單，一如以往有很多韓國男星入選，今年亦有不少台灣男星上榜，例如林宥嘉、周渝民（仔仔）、張孝全、陳柏霖及王大陸等。而香港男星只有四位上榜，分別是出名靚仔的關智斌（Kenny）、黃宗澤（Bosco）、憑劇集《三十而已》而在內地走紅的馬志威，還有這位最近如沐春風的TVB男藝人，實行同玄彬、崔始源，李敏鎬鬥靚仔。"},{"pid":"64d965875f6624dd7e0e520ef5d30557ed1ff6e3","tid":2216154,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":17,"score":-17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T13:00:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385787594371371008.jpeg/QO7hsLAKzkp5TXGYGtBxsfCWFpw2RZAhWW5-EFlufhA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385787594371371008.jpeg%2FQO7hsLAKzkp5TXGYGtBxsfCWFpw2RZAhWW5-EFlufhA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=5bc312f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385787596653072385.jpeg/ztGLuZQDxEAeBGv1MT2OyCu4kMxJnTGUAcz0LQHM9C0?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385787596653072385.jpeg%2FztGLuZQDxEAeBGv1MT2OyCu4kMxJnTGUAcz0LQHM9C0%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=42adea8e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385787577388634112.jpeg/CGRCBGqHVDdbtOOA_9N3WGQYNZolBGAnxmFwgsZhcII?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385787577388634112.jpeg%2FCGRCBGqHVDdbtOOA_9N3WGQYNZolBGAnxmFwgsZhcII%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=1ffc94f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385787579599032320.jpeg/vAmmpL0y37YmVK